			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Smarterer is looking for a sales rep to help turn the traditional skills-testing model on its head by selling our newly-launched product, SkillSets. SkillSets helps recruiters and hiring managers hire smarter by quickly identifying the most skilled candidates.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>If you&rsquo;re right the right person if:</strong></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;">
&bull; You love everything about selling - prospecting, calls, presenting value, and closing.<br />
&bull; You&rsquo;re pioneering - you love to strike out into uncharted territory in pursuit of a huge reward.<br />
&bull; You love working in a startup environment where things move fast.<br />
&bull; You&rsquo;re assertive, hungry, and smart as hell.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>Here&#39;s what you&#39;ll do day to day:</strong></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;">
&bull; Close sales (you&rsquo;re a revenue-producing machine!)<br />
&bull; Prospect like an animal (you know the drill.)<br />
&bull; Share what you&rsquo;ve learned with our marketing and product teams.</p>
<p>
<strong>A few Must-Haves:</strong></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;">
&bull; You&rsquo;ve got &quot;hustle&quot; - passion, commitment, and amazing work ethic.<br />
&bull; 2-4 years experience in inside sales, selling SaaS/web technology in a B2B environment.<br />
&bull; Strong prospecting and closing skills.<br />
&bull; You know how to forecast and manage a pipeline.<br />
&bull; Strong office software skills. HubSpot is a plus.<br />
&bull; You&rsquo;re articulate and write very well.<br />
&bull; You&#39;re exceptionally bright and extremely goal-oriented.<br />
&bull; You&rsquo;ve worked in a startup so you understand the urgency required.<br />
&bull; You&#39;re enthusiastic, positive, and a lot of fun to work with!</p>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
Is this you? Tell us why! Send us your resume and cover letter, and be sure to tell us about your prior sales successes!</p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;">
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
---------</p>
<p>
Smarterer scores digital, social, and technical skills using crowdsourced test design and an adaptive scoring algorithm. In the past year, Smarterer users have taken more than 2 million tests and answered 20 million questions.&nbsp; Our vision: Become the global standard in skills measurement. The opportunity? Huge!&nbsp;</p>
<p>
Smarterer is backed by Google Ventures and True Ventures.</p>
