<p>
Smarterer is seeking a smart, motivated Account Management Intern. We&rsquo;re an early-stage consumer web startup based in Boston&rsquo;s South End, funded by True Ventures, Google Ventures, and and a group of top-tier angels. This role will give you significant exposure to the inner workings of a startup.</p>
<p>
You&rsquo;ll work closely with our Marketing team to help grow Smarterer&rsquo;s presence in the education 2.0 space. Here&rsquo;s what you&rsquo;ll be doing:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Work 15-30 hours per week from our awesome offices in the South End</li>
<li>
Conduct outreach calls to site users and job recruiters to drive user acquisition and gather platform feedback</li>
<li>
Research and identify key influencers and community members in the recruiting and online learning industries</li>
<li>
Dive into in the tech startup community in Boston.</li>
<li>
Most importantly, you will be learning &ndash; we take this seriously, and we&rsquo;ll work together to ensure that you gain tremendous experience inside and outside of the office. In addition to all the cool projects you will be working on, as an intern at Smarterer you will have access to unlimited free Intelligent.ly classes!</li>
</ul>
<p>
<br />
If you&rsquo;re enthusiastic, have great phone manner, work independently and creatively, love technology, and are passionate about creating a successful consumer web business, apply! &nbsp;Be sure to submit your resume and a cover letter with answers to the following questions:</p>
<ul>
<li>
What is your favorite social media platform?</li>
<li>
